00041 #define DEBUG_SUBSYSTEM S_LOV

00043 #include "lov_cl_internal.h"

00049 /*****************************************************************************
00050  *
00051  * Lovsub lock operations.
00052  *
00053  */
00054 
00055 static void lovsub_lock_fini(const struct lu_env *env,
00056                              struct cl_lock_slice *slice)
00057 {
00058         struct lovsub_lock   *lsl;
00059 
00060         ENTRY;
00061         lsl = cl2lovsub_lock(slice);
00062         LASSERT(list_empty(&lsl->lss_parents));
00063         OBD_SLAB_FREE_PTR(lsl, lovsub_lock_kmem);
00064         EXIT;
00065 }
00066 
00067 static const struct cl_lock_operations lovsub_lock_ops = {
00068         .clo_fini    = lovsub_lock_fini,
00069 };
00070 
00071 int lovsub_lock_init(const struct lu_env *env, struct cl_object *obj,
00072                      struct cl_lock *lock, const struct cl_io *io)
00073 {
00074         struct lovsub_lock *lsk;
00075         int result;
00076 
00077         ENTRY;
00078         OBD_SLAB_ALLOC_PTR_GFP(lsk, lovsub_lock_kmem, GFP_NOFS);
00079         if (lsk != NULL) {
00080                 INIT_LIST_HEAD(&lsk->lss_parents);
00081                 cl_lock_slice_add(lock, &lsk->lss_cl, obj, &lovsub_lock_ops);
00082                 result = 0;
00083         } else
00084                 result = -ENOMEM;
00085         RETURN(result);
00086 }
